g2:c.BORDERLESS-FREE-TEXT.g2:a.TEXT: Awaiting grammar for wait until -- not yet provided.

Modified the test to wait for 30 seconds after invoking the rule category. The original 2 second wait was not always long enough to succeed. The tests could be slowed down depending on machine load. Also, update the timeout-limit attribute of activation-1. - cpm, 3/4/92

g2:c.PROCEDURE.g2:a.TEXT:
text-values-3-test (node : class benchmark-node)
begin if not (the text of the font-for-descriptions of fonts = "small" or the text of the font-for-descriptions of fonts = "large") then call fail (node, "Failed to get font-for-description of fonts.")
else if the text of the default-priority-for-runtime-saving of saving-parameters /= "8" then call fail (node, "Failed to get default-priority-for-runtime-saving of saving-parameters system table.") else call pass (node); end

g2:c.RULE.g2:a.TEXT:
for any symbol S that is an inferior-class of class-expressions-designator
for any item ITM that is of the class named by S unconditionally conclude that the age of ITM = the age of ITM + 1
